snippet: FOREIGN IRON.--An official table published in The Philadelphia North American, shows that, after the first year of the operation of the Tariff of 46, the imports of iron doubled at a single bound, and have been steadily increasing ever since....
lead_paragraph: FOREIGN IRON.--An official table published in The Philadelphia North American, shows that, after the first year of the operation of the Tariff of 46, the imports of iron doubled at a single bound, and have been steadily increasing ever since.
